<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>商品案内｜鶴田酒店</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@400;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    /* ─── カラー定義（元サイト準拠） ─── */
    :root{
      --bg:#c8dfff;          /* 元サイト #a4d1ff を少し明るく */
      --bg2:#ddeeff;
      --navy:#000099;        /* 元サイトのリンク文字色 */
      --blue:#0055cc;
      --orange:#e86400;      /* 元サイトのリンク色 */
      --red:#cc0000;
      --text:#1a2a5a;
      --border:#88b8ee;
      --white:#f4f9ff;
      --card:#ffffff;
      --gold:#b8882a;        /* オリジナル商品強調用 */
      --gold-l:#d4a84b;
      --muted:#4a6080;
    }
    *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
    body{
      background:var(--bg);
      color:var(--text);
      font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;
      font-weight:300;
      min-height:100vh;
    }
    /* 元サイト風ドットパターン背景 */
    body::before{
      content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;
      background-image:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(0,80,200,0.12) 1px,transparent 1px);
      background-size:20px 20px;
      pointer-events:none;z-index:0;
    }
    .page-wrap{position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:480px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 0 100px;}

    /* ─── ヘッダー ─── */
    .header{
      background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--navy) 0%,#0033aa 100%);
      padding:28px 20px 22px;text-align:center;position:relative;
    }
    .header::before{
      content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;
      background-image:repeating-linear-gradient(45deg,transparent,transparent 8px,rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 8px,rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 9px);
    }
    .header::after{
      content:'';position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;
      background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--orange),#ffaa44,var(--orange));
    }
    .header-label{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.35em;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);margin-bottom:8px;position:relative;}
    .header-title{font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;line-height:1.4;letter-spacing:0.05em;position:relative;}
    .header-sub{font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);margin-top:6px;letter-spacing:0.1em;position:relative;}

    /* ─── カテゴリナビ ─── */
    .nav{
      position:sticky;top:0;z-index:50;
      background:rgba(0,0,153,0.95);
      backdrop-filter:blur(8px);
      border-bottom:2px solid var(--orange);
      overflow-x:auto;scrollbar-width:none;
    }
    .nav::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none;}
    .nav-inner{display:inline-flex;min-width:100%;}
    .nav-btn{
      background:none;border:none;
      color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
      font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-size:12px;
      padding:11px 13px;cursor:pointer;white-space:nowrap;
      border-bottom:3px solid transparent;
      transition:all 0.2s;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;
    }
    .nav-btn.active{color:#fff;border-bottom-color:var(--orange);}

    /* ─── 注意書き ─── */
    .note-box{
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      border-left:4px solid var(--orange);
      border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;
      padding:12px 14px;font-size:12px;
      color:var(--text);line-height:1.8;
      margin:16px 14px 0;
    }
    .note-box strong{color:var(--red);}

    /* ─── セクションラベル ─── */
    .sec-label{
      display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
      padding:18px 14px 10px;
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
      margin-top:4px;
    }
    .sec-bar{width:5px;height:24px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--orange),var(--red));border-radius:3px;flex-shrink:0;}
    .sec-title{font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);}
    .sec-sub{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:2px;}

    /* ─── カード（汎用） ─── */
    .card{
      background:var(--card);margin:14px 14px 0;
      border-radius:12px;border:1px solid var(--border);
      overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,50,150,0.1);
    }
    .card-head{
      background:var(--navy);padding:12px 18px;
      display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
    }
    .card-head-bar{width:5px;height:18px;background:var(--orange);border-radius:3px;flex-shrink:0;}
    .card-head-title{font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:14px;color:#fff;letter-spacing:0.08em;}
    .card-head-sub{font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45);margin-top:2px;}

    /* ─── 商品アイテム ─── */
	 #list-kokubun { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 5px; padding: 5px; } 
	 #list-hamada { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 5px; padding: 5px; } 
	 #list-shirogane { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 5px; padding: 5px; } 
	 #list-others { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 5px; padding: 5px; } 
	 #list-limited { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 5px; padding: 5px; }
	 #list-premier { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 5px; padding: 5px; } 
    .prod-item{border-bottom:1px solid #ddeeff;overflow:hidden;}
    .prod-item:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
    .prod-item.sold-out{opacity:0.55;}
    /* 画像は自然な縦横比のまま */
    .prod-img{width:100%;height:auto;aspect-ratio:1/1;object-fit:contain;display:block;background:#ddeeff;}
    .prod-body{padding:14px 16px;}
    .badges{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:5px;margin-bottom:8px;}
    .badge{font-size:10px;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:20px;font-weight:500;}
    .badge-sold{background:#ddd;color:#777;border:1px solid #bbb;}
    .badge-limit{background:rgba(204,0,0,0.08);color:var(--red);border:1px solid rgba(204,0,0,0.2);}
    .badge-new{background:rgba(0,100,0,0.08);color:#005000;border:1px solid rgba(0,100,0,0.2);}
    .badge-rare{background:rgba(184,136,42,0.1);color:#7a5c10;border:1px solid rgba(184,136,42,0.25);}
    .prod-name{font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:2px;line-height:1.3;}
    .prod-kura{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:9px;letter-spacing:0.05em;}
    .prod-desc{font-size:12px;color:var(--text);line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:12px;}
    .prices{background:var(--bg2);border-radius:8px;border:1px solid var(--border);overflow:hidden;}
    .price-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:8px 13px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(136,184,238,0.4);}
    .price-row:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
    .price-size{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);}
    .price-val{font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:var(--orange);}

    /* ─── オリジナル商品（特別デザイン） ─── */
	#original-list { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 5px; padding: 5px; } 
	#nonbiyori-list { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 5px; padding: 5px; }  
    .orig-card{
      background:linear-gradient(160deg,var(--navy) 0%,#002288 100%);
      margin:14px 14px 0;border-radius:12px;
      border:2px solid var(--orange);
      overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,100,0.2);
    }
    .orig-head{padding:18px 18px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(232,100,0,0.2);}
    .orig-ruby{font-size:10px;color:var(--orange);letter-spacing:0.3em;margin-bottom:5px;font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;}
    .orig-name{font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:21px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;line-height:1.4;}
    .orig-tag{font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45);margin-top:5px;line-height:1.7;}
    .orig-item {
	  padding:5px;
	  border:1px solid rgba(232,100,0,0.1);
	  border-radius:8px;
	}
    .orig-item:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
    /* オリジナルの画像も自然な縦横比 */
    .orig-img{width:100%;height:auto;aspect-ratio:1/1;object-fit:contain;display:block;margin-bottom:10px;border-radius:6px;}
    .orig-iname{font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--gold-l);margin-bottom:3px;}
    .orig-idesc{font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);margin-bottom:9px;line-height:1.7;}
    .orig-prices{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:7px;}
    .orig-ptag{background:rgba(232,100,0,0.15);border:1px solid rgba(232,100,0,0.3);border-radius:7px;padding:6px 12px;text-align:center;}
    .orig-psize{font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);display:block;margin-bottom:2px;}
    .orig-pval{font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--orange);}

    /* ─── おつまみ提案 ─── */
    .pair-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:11px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid #ddeeff;font-size:13px;color:var(--text);}
    .pair-item:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
    .pair-icon{font-size:22px;width:32px;text-align:center;flex-shrink:0;}
    .pair-note{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:2px;}
    .pair-foot{padding:12px 16px;background:var(--bg2);font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.8;border-top:1px solid var(--border);}

    /* ─── フッター ─── */
    .footer{text-align:center;padding:20px 16px 16px;font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);line-height:2;}
    .admin-open-btn{margin-top:12px;display:inline-block;font-size:10px;color:rgba(0,0,153,0.35);background:none;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,153,0.15);border-radius:6px;padding:4px 12px;cursor:pointer;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;}

    /* ─── 固定CTAバー ─── */
    .cta-bar{position:fixed;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:100;background:rgba(0,0,153,0.97);backdrop-filter:blur(10px);border-top:2px solid var(--orange);padding:12px 14px;display:flex;gap:10px;}
    .cta-btn{flex:1;padding:13px;border-radius:9px;font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.08em;cursor:pointer;text-align:center;text-decoration:none;display:block;}
    .cta-primary{background:var(--orange);border:none;color:#fff;}
    .cta-secondary{background:none;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);font-size:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;}

    /* ─── パスワードモーダル ─── */
    .pw-overlay{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:150;background:rgba(0,0,80,0.85);align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:20px;}
    .pw-overlay.show{display:flex;}
    .pw-box{background:var(--white);border-radius:14px;padding:28px 22px;max-width:300px;width:100%;text-align:center;border:2px solid var(--orange);}
    .pw-title{font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:15px;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:6px;}
    .pw-sub{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:14px;}
    .pw-input{width:100%;padding:12px;border:2px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;font-size:20px;text-align:center;letter-spacing:0.3em;margin-bottom:10px;-webkit-appearance:none;background:white;color:var(--navy);}
    .pw-input:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--orange);}
    .pw-err{font-size:12px;color:var(--red);margin-bottom:8px;min-height:18px;}
    .pw-submit{width:100%;padding:13px;background:var(--orange);border:none;border-radius:8px;color:#fff;font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:14px;cursor:pointer;margin-bottom:10px;letter-spacing:0.08em;}
    .pw-cancel{background:none;border:none;color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;cursor:pointer;padding:4px;}

    /* ─── 管理パネル ─── */
    .admin-overlay{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:200;background:rgba(0,0,40,0.97);flex-direction:column;overflow:hidden;}
    .admin-overlay.show{display:flex;}
    .admin-head{background:#00008a;border-bottom:2px solid var(--orange);padding:14px 18px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-shrink:0;}
    .admin-title{font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:15px;color:var(--orange);letter-spacing:0.1em;}
    .admin-close{background:none;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);border-radius:7px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);padding:7px 14px;font-size:12px;cursor:pointer;}
    .admin-body{flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:14px;}
    .admin-notice{background:rgba(232,100,0,0.12);border:1px solid rgba(232,100,0,0.35);border-radius:9px;padding:13px 15px;font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);line-height:1.9;margin-bottom:18px;}
    .admin-notice strong{color:var(--orange);}
    .admin-url-row{display:flex;gap:7px;margin-top:10px;}
    .admin-url-in{flex:1;padding:9px 11px;background:#000055;border:1px solid #334499;border-radius:6px;color:#fff;font-size:13px;}
    .admin-url-save{padding:9px 13px;background:var(--orange);border:none;border-radius:6px;color:#fff;font-size:12px;cursor:pointer;white-space:nowrap;}
    .admin-add-btn{display:block;width:100%;padding:13px;background:none;border:2px dashed var(--orange);border-radius:9px;color:var(--orange);font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:13px;cursor:pointer;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:14px;}
    .admin-gl{font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);letter-spacing:0.1em;padding:8px 4px 4px;}
    .admin-item{background:#0a0a3a;border:1px solid #223366;border-radius:8px;padding:10px 11px;margin-bottom:5px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;}
    .admin-iinfo{flex:1;min-width:0;}
    .admin-iname{font-size:12px;color:#fff;font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;}
    .admin-isub{font-size:10px;color:#889;margin-top:1px;}
    .admin-iprice{font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:13px;color:var(--orange);white-space:nowrap;}
    .admin-ibtns{display:flex;gap:4px;flex-shrink:0;}
    .a-btn{border:none;border-radius:5px;padding:5px 8px;font-size:10px;cursor:pointer;}
    .a-btn.stock{background:#0a2a0a;color:#5c5;border:1px solid #0a400a;}
    .a-btn.soldout{background:#2a2a2a;color:#888;border:1px solid #333;}
    .a-btn.edit{background:#1a1a2a;color:#aac;border:1px solid #334;}
    .a-btn.del{background:#2a0a0a;color:#e55;border:1px solid #400a0a;}
    .admin-reset{display:block;width:100%;padding:11px;margin-top:18px;background:none;border:1px solid #334;border-radius:7px;color:#558;font-size:11px;cursor:pointer;}

    /* ─── 商品編集モーダル ─── */
    .edit-overlay{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:300;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.88);align-items:flex-end;justify-content:center;}
    .edit-overlay.show{display:flex;}
    .edit-modal{background:#0a0a3a;border-radius:18px 18px 0 0;border:1px solid #334;padding:22px 18px 38px;width:100%;max-width:480px;max-height:92vh;overflow-y:auto;}
    .edit-title{font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:15px;color:var(--orange);letter-spacing:0.08em;margin-bottom:18px;}
    .ef{margin-bottom:13px;}
    .ef label{font-size:10px;color:#889;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin-bottom:5px;display:block;}
    .ef input,.ef textarea{width:100%;padding:10px 12px;background:#000055;border:1.5px solid #334;border-radius:7px;color:#fff;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-size:15px;-webkit-appearance:none;}
    .ef input:focus,.ef textarea:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--orange);}
    .ef textarea{min-height:72px;resize:vertical;font-size:13px;}
    .ef-row{display:flex;gap:9px;}
    .ef-row .ef{flex:1;}
    .check-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;padding:9px 0;}
    .check-row label{margin:0;font-size:12px;color:#ccd;}
    .check-row input[type="checkbox"]{width:18px;height:18px;accent-color:var(--orange);cursor:pointer;}
    .edit-btns{display:flex;gap:9px;margin-top:18px;}
    .e-save{flex:1;padding:13px;background:var(--orange);border:none;border-radius:7px;font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#fff;cursor:pointer;}
    .e-cancel{padding:13px 18px;background:none;border:1px solid #445;border-radius:7px;color:#889;font-size:13px;cursor:pointer;}

    /* ─── 完了モーダル ─── */
    .done-overlay{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:100;background:rgba(0,0,80,0.85);align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:20px;}
    .done-overlay.show{display:flex;}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page-wrap">

  <div class="header">
    <div class="header-label">PRODUCT GUIDE</div>
    <div class="header-title">商品案内</div>
    <div class="header-sub">鶴田酒店｜地酒・本格焼酎の専門店</div>
  </div>

  <nav class="nav">
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <button class="nav-btn active" onclick="navTo('sec-original',this)">当店オリジナル</button>
      <button class="nav-btn" onclick="navTo('sec-kokubun',this)">国分酒造</button>
      <button class="nav-btn" onclick="navTo('sec-hamada',this)">濱田酒造</button>
      <button class="nav-btn" onclick="navTo('sec-shirogane',this)">白金酒造</button>
      <button class="nav-btn" onclick="navTo('sec-others',this)">その他</button>
      <button class="nav-btn" onclick="navTo('sec-limited',this)">鹿児島限定</button>
      <button class="nav-btn" onclick="navTo('sec-pairing',this)">おつまみ提案</button>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div class="note-box">
    全て<strong>税込価格</strong>です。商品によっては入手困難・仕込中のものもあります。他にも色々取り揃えておりますのでお問い合わせください。
  </div>

  <!-- ── 当店オリジナル ── -->
  <div id="sec-original">

    <div class="orig-card">
      <div class="orig-head">
        <div class="orig-ruby">まぼろしの ごせっきょう</div>
        <div class="orig-name">幻の五石橋</div>
        <div class="orig-tag">当店だけのオリジナル焼酎。店主が割水・味・口当たり・デザイン等、全てにこだわった焼酎です。<br>平成7年の大水害で流出した甲突川の五大石橋を忘れないようにとの思いを込めて。</div>
      </div>
      <div id="original-list"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="orig-card" id="nonbiyori-card" style="margin-top:10px;">
      <div class="orig-head">
        <div class="orig-ruby">のんびより</div>
        <div class="orig-name">飲ん日和</div>
        <div class="orig-tag">桜島の絵をラベルにし、まさに鹿児島をイメージした焼酎。黒こうじ造り。<br>『飲んびよい　燃えて色づく　桜島』</div>
      </div>
      <div id="nonbiyori-list"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- ── プレミア焼酎 ── -->
  <div id="sec-premier">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-head"><div class="card-head-bar"></div><div><div class="card-head-title">プレミア焼酎</div></div></div>
      <div id="list-premier"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- ── 国分酒造 ── -->
  <div id="sec-kokubun">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-head"><div class="card-head-bar"></div><div><div class="card-head-title">国分酒造</div></div></div>
      <div id="list-kokubun"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── 濱田酒造 ── -->
  <div id="sec-hamada">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-head"><div class="card-head-bar"></div><div><div class="card-head-title">濱田酒造</div></div></div>
      <div id="list-hamada"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── 白金酒造 ── -->
  <div id="sec-shirogane">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-head"><div class="card-head-bar"></div><div><div class="card-head-title">白金酒造</div></div></div>
      <div id="list-shirogane"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── その他 ── -->
  <div id="sec-others">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-head"><div class="card-head-bar"></div><div><div class="card-head-title">その他の銘柄</div></div></div>
      <div id="list-others"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── 鹿児島限定 ── -->
  <div id="sec-limited">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-head"><div class="card-head-bar"></div><div>
